body_html:
@Conceptron @cy89 thanks for reporting this issue. I believe this has to do with some subtle differences among the two markdown renderers that we have:

  1. The one on GitHub
  2. The one on the tensorflow.org website.

This file renders correctly on GitHub:
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/docs_src/programmers_guide/debugger.md

cc @MarkDaoust for any possible insight.
